{
  "type": "excalidraw",
  "version": 2,
  "source": "claude",
  "elements": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 20,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 40,
      "text": "Shape 2 — Toolbox with OAuth Passthrough (user token never touches the agent)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "spfx",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 90,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 100,
      "strokeColor": "#0078D4",
      "backgroundColor": "#CFE4FA",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{ "type": "text", "id": "spfx_t" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "spfx_t",
      "containerId": "spfx",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 110,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "1  SPFx web part (React) — SharePoint, user's browser\nAadHttpClient -> user AAD token\nrenders \"Grant access\" card + window.open() on -32007",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "proxy",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 250,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 95,
      "strokeColor": "#F7630C",
      "backgroundColor": "#FFF4CE",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{ "type": "text", "id": "proxy_t" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "proxy_t",
      "containerId": "proxy",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 268,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "2  Azure Function — thin proxy  /api/agent/chat  (NO OBO here)\nforwards the question to the agent\ncatches -32007 -> returns {consentRequired, consentUrl} to SPFx",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "foundry",
      "x": 340,
      "y": 405,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 470,
      "strokeColor": "#107C10",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 3,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "foundry_lbl",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 415,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 28,
      "text": "Microsoft Foundry  (cloud)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "agent",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 455,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 95,
      "strokeColor": "#107C10",
      "backgroundColor": "#DFF6DD",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{ "type": "text", "id": "agent_t" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "agent_t",
      "containerId": "agent",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 473,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "3  Hosted Agent  (F5 locally for debug; deployed in prod)\nattaches the toolbox  -  model inference: gpt-4.x\ncarries ONLY its own ai.azure.com token",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "toolbox",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 575,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 75,
      "strokeColor": "#0C8599",
      "backgroundColor": "#99E9F2",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{ "type": "text", "id": "toolbox_t" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "toolbox_t",
      "containerId": "toolbox",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 590,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 45,
      "text": "4  Toolbox  (preview: Foundry-Features: Toolboxes=V1Preview)\nmcp tool entry -> project_connection_id",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "conn",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 675,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 120,
      "strokeColor": "#5C2D91",
      "backgroundColor": "#E8DAEF",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{ "type": "text", "id": "conn_t" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "conn_t",
      "containerId": "conn",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 693,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 84,
      "text": "5  OAuth2 RemoteTool connection  (generic_mcp)\nBYO client_id/secret = OBO app reg\nper-user consent + token store\nINJECTS the user's delegated token into the outbound call",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "mcp",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 935,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 115,
      "strokeColor": "#862E9C",
      "backgroundColor": "#F3D9FA",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{ "type": "text", "id": "mcp_t" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "mcp_t",
      "containerId": "mcp",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 953,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "6  YOUR custom MCP server  (Container App / dev tunnel for local)\nexposes tools/list + tools/call\nget_sharepoint_profile  + other on-behalf-of-user tools\nreads the USER token from the inbound request (NO DefaultAzureCredential)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "graph",
      "x": 380,
      "y": 1095,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 75,
      "strokeColor": "#0C8599",
      "backgroundColor": "#99E9F2",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{ "type": "text", "id": "graph_t" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "graph_t",
      "containerId": "graph",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 1110,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 45,
      "text": "7  Microsoft Graph  /  SharePoint UPS\nPeopleManager/GetMyProperties  (acts AS THE USER)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "entra",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 675,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 175,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "#DEE2E6",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "boundElements": [{ "type": "text", "id": "entra_t" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "entra_t",
      "containerId": "entra",
      "x": 1030,
      "y": 695,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "8  Entra OBO app registration\nclient_id/secret used by connection #5\ndelegated scopes:\n  Graph User.Read  -  SP AllSites.Read ...\nrenders the standard consent screen\nat the -32007 URL",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle"
    },

    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "legend",
      "x": 1020,
      "y": 90,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 470,
      "strokeColor": "#1E1E1E",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "legend_t",
      "x": 1038,
      "y": 108,
      "width": 330,
      "height": 430,
      "text": "TOKEN LEGEND (who carries what)\n\n(a) SPFx -> proxy\n    user AAD token (access_as_user)\n    = the user\n\n(b) proxy -> agent\n    ai.azure.com/.default\n    = proxy/app\n\n(c) agent -> toolbox\n    ai.azure.com/.default\n    = the AGENT (never the user)\n\n(d) connection -> MCP server\n    USER delegated token (injected)\n    = the user\n\n(d') MCP server -> Graph\n    same user token = the user\n\nKEY: the user's token appears\nonly at (a) and (d). It NEVER\ntouches the agent (c). Foundry's\nconnection layer (#5) is the only\nplace user identity is re-materialized.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },

    {
      "type": "arrow",
      "id": "a_spfx_proxy",
      "x": 660,
      "y": 192,
      "width": 0,
      "height": 56,
      "strokeColor": "#0078D4",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "points": [[0, 0], [0, 56]],
      "startBinding": { "elementId": "spfx", "focus": 0, "gap": 2 },
      "endBinding": { "elementId": "proxy", "focus": 0, "gap": 2 }
    },
